## Context

- Task 849 (cluster stability): COMPLETED. Ran full CMTF + MOFA2 integration and consensus clustering on HMP2 data (76 participants: 50 CD, 26 nonIBD; 246 species, 80898 metabolites after QC).
- NEGATIVE RESULT: CMTF silhouette scores 0.12-0.14 (all below 0.3 threshold). MOFA2 best sil=0.288 at k=2, near but below threshold. Permutation test p=1.0 (not significant). Collection site is a confounder (PERMANOVA F=3.36, p=0.001).
- Root causes: (1) 80K metabolites vs 76 samples (overcomplete), (2) site confounding, (3) small n.
